<!-- article body start -->

<p>Here is a fun section of The Smog where readers like you&mdash;yes, you&mdash;can help shape future issues of The Smog and also get some cool prizes. To send in your answers, please send a private message to the Smogon user <a href="/forums/member.php?u=32443">The Smog</a> titled "Issue 6 Polls/Trivia" with answers to any or all questions.</p>
<p>Trivia has returned! This month, none of the trivia is multiple choice, so you have to figure out the answers yourself.</p>
<p>Good luck!</p>

<ol>
<li style="margin-top: 1em;">Name every set of Pokemon that has identical base stats.</li>
<li style="margin-top: 1em;">Name every move that has changed Type from one generation to another.</li>
<li style="margin-top: 1em;">Name every Flying-type Pokemon that does not learn Roost. (Not counting Arceus or Kecleon)</li>
<li style="margin-top: 1em;">Name every move that changed from physical to special between generations 3 and 4.</li>
<li style="margin-top: 1em;">Name every ability that does nothing in battles.</li>
<li style="margin-top: 1em;">Name every Pokemon that evolves into two or more Pokemon.</li>
<li style="margin-top: 1em;">Name every Pokemon lighter than 1 Pound.</li>
<li style="margin-top: 1em;">Name every Pokemon that has been OU since RBY. </li>
</ol>

